{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is <strong>Posthaste</strong>; arcade-style, fast-paced rally racing game. Developed by a solo dev, this game aims to deliver a challenging, yet entertaining experience to its players. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Fundamentals of Posthaste</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Haste Meter</strong> <strong>-</strong> <strong>Posthaste</strong> adds a new mechanic to arcade rally racing: <strong>Haste Meter</strong>. You can fill your <strong>Haste Meter</strong> by drifting and driving at high speeds. With your <strong>Haste Meter</strong> full, you'll be able to initiate <strong>ProBoost</strong>.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>ProBoost</strong> <strong>-</strong> The <strong>ProBoost</strong> feature allows you to have a major 10-second speed boost, which becomes available after filling up your <strong>Haste Meter</strong>.  <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576440/extras/Hastemeter-ezgif.com-resize__1_.gif?t=1736105353\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Boost</strong> <strong>-</strong> Filling up over time, the Boost feature can give your car either slow or instant burst of acceleration depending on which Boost type you choose, including Default (Instant), Snappy (Instant), and Burn (Slow).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576440/extras/BoostDemonstration-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1736105353\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Configuration - </strong>Basic configuration options for changing the Boost mode and adjusting transmission ratios are available.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Car Mods - </strong>Simple modification options such as Boost Refill and Lightweight Body are included to give you an advantage which can be unlocked by driving.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Other currently available content</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 3 Maps/Stages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 4 Rally Cars </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 7 Steam Achievements to unlock</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Last One Standing","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2576440/e80a1aa197296c0bcc863869023d9b6d7c8d89fd.jpg"},{"name":"Deal!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2576440/f783661d3635fc60764da2711c3251071ff28006.jpg"},{"name":"Bought the Dealership","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2576440/eb8a8cb7860b32453105f156be0aa145ebb9ef55.jpg"},{"name":"Like New","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2576440/78fa868dc75d0ce23b0246a014bf812f79f129a6.jpg"},{"name":"Speedster","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2576440/25867ae0cb01da6d534b133d50888f58b1b82629.jpg"},{"name":"Posthaste!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2576440/e55945f0f1c9d9d6ede590935deca9511c9ac00f.jpg"},{"name":"Challenger","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2576440/5c27ca1a2d7b4261af89fcf17a97b7da995cea2e.jpg"}],"total":7},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576440/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736105353","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576440/page.bg.jpg?t=1736105353","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576440/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736105353","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576440/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736105353","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Par